bug.short_desc: "Insert in Layout" is disabled for dimensions and measures in Data Explorer Viewer [00]

long_desc.thetext:
Description: "Insert in Layout" is disabled for dimensions and measures in Data Explorer Viewer.
Build number: 2.3.0.v20080110-0800
Steps to reproduce: 1. New a cube and a crosstab. 2. Select the crosstab row area cell or column area cell. 3. In the Data Explorer View, right click the Group or Measure.
Expected result: "Insert in Layout" is enabled.
Actual result: "Insert in Layout" is disabled.
Error log: N/A
Currently Dimension and Level don't support "insert in layout" action. The behavior depends on particular container.
